{"id": "art-181", "label": "Art. 181", "title": "Art. 181", "slug": "art-181", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 181 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_259242905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1982\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_259242905\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>,\nrespectiv directoratul, trebuie s&#259; prezinte cenzorilor, respectiv auditorilor\ninterni <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> auditorilor financiari, cu cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> 30 de zile înainte de ziua stabilit&#259; pentru\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;edin&#355;a</span> adun&#259;rii generale <span\nclass=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259; anual&#259; pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>exerci&#355;iul</span> financiar precedent, <span class=SpellE>înso&#355;it&#259;</span>\nde raportul lor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de documentele justificative.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}